Hictu,is,a,video,microblogging,site,It,provides,an,API,for,retrieving,video,posts,and,user,profiles,as,well,as,the,ability,to,post,text,video,messages,The,basic,API,does,not,require,an,API,Key,and,is,read,only,The,Advanced,API,allows,users,access,to,the,Hictu,platform,with,write,permission,Using,this,method,users,can,post,their,thoughts,on,the,home,page,or,share,videos